Your MMDVMHost config (/etc/mmdvmhost) should have the following set for your chosen layout.

G4KLX Layouts:
[Nextion]
ScreenLayout=1

GB2OE Layouts:
[Nextion]
ScreenLayout=1

ON7LDS L2:
[Nextion]
ScreenLayout=2

ON7LDS L3:
[Nextion]
ScreenLayout=4

ON7LDS ND-L3:
*Note: Requires NextionDriver
[Nextion]
ScreenLayout=4

